mdes.slick.sui
Interface Theme

All Known Implementing Classes:
BitterLemonTheme, CopperTheme, SteelAcidTheme, SteelBlueTheme, SteelSepiaTheme
public interface Theme

Buttons, text fields and windows are rendered using the colors defined in the current Theme.

Themes in Sui will be reworked shortly.

See Also:
mdes.slick.sui.Sui#setTheme(SuiTheme)
